Package au.com.team2moro.couchdbsyncer Description

couchdbsyncer - syncs couchdb databases from the server, saving documents and attachments locally in an sqlite database.

DatabaseStore handles the storage of documents and attachments from one or more CouchDB databases. Applications will typically create a single shared instance of DatabaseStore. a Syncer object is used to synchronize a local database with a remote CouchDB database. SyncerService can be subclassed to provide a IntentService to run a syncer update.
